verbs.description: at three local churches the spirit of celebration upward of 20 000 people [V: are] expected to celebrate the culture and food of armenia greece and poland this weekend during festivals at three capital region churches they are a hungry lot st peter armenian apostolic church in watervliet where its festival runs saturday and sunday served up 900 pounds of lamb alone during a previous year event the meat tally this year for the festival with an 80-plus - year tradition will exceed 1 200 pounds according to festival co - cordinator charles tutunjian the number of food trays will extend into the many hundreds and individual pastries to the many thousands at st st peter armenian apostolic church saratoga springs high school ron brosnihan blessed virgin mary of czestochowa church blessed virgin mary polishfest charles tutunjian anntonette zembrzuski alberti greece blessed virgin mary of czestochowa
